issue.title: DART joint springs are partially working.

content.raw:
I merged branch `gazebo_dart` (it is closed now) back to my fork `gazebo_3.0_dart_4.0` branch. It is compiling with dart [`inverse_kinematics` branch](https://github.com/dartsim/dart/pull/154). It will be merged back to master branch soon.

Also I split gazebo_dart branch into `gazebo_2.2_dart_3.0` and `gazebo_3.0_dart_4.0` to keep supporting DART 3.0 for Gazebo 2.2.
